column3: Little interest or pleasure in doing things
column5: Trouble falling or staying asleep, or sleeping too much
column6: Feeling tired or having little energy
column8: Feeling bad about yourself—or that you are a failure or have let yourself or your family down
column9: Trouble concentrating on things, such as reading the newspaper or watching television
column10: Moving or speaking so slowly that other people could have noticed? Or the opposite—being so fidgety or restless that you have been moving around a lot more than usual
